The output is an array of length `num_people`.
The sum of all elements in the output array is equal to `candies`.
The first element in the output array is the sum of all candies given on the first turn.
The second element in the output array is the sum of all candies given on the second turn.
The third element in the output array is the sum of all candies given on the third turn.
The last element in the output array is the sum of all remaining candies.
